fwd: relative path to forward fastqs of raw data can be multiple fastqs spearated by “;”
rev: relative path to rev fastqs of raw data can be multiple fastqs spearated by “;” in the same order the “fwd”
unp: relative path to unpaired fastqs of raw data can be multiple fastqs spearated by “;”
read_subset: number of read subset for subset library (optional)
sortmerna_refs: database for sortmeRNA --- can be multiple paths spearated by “;” (optional)
